check - Runs all checks.
checkDocLinks - Verifies that every repo-local link in Markdown documentation resolves
checkstyle - Runs checkstyle on all subprojects
diff - Tests GraalVM Reflection Metadata that was changed between 'baseCommit' and 'newCommit'
jacocoTestReport - Generates JaCoCo coverage reports for all subprojects (runs tests first)
javaTest - Runs JVM tests (Gradle 'test') for all subprojects
runNativeTraceImage - Runs trace-enabled native tests once for matching coordinates
spotlessApply - Applies code formatting steps to sourcecode in-place.
spotlessCheck - Checks that sourcecode satisfies formatting steps.
spotlessDiagnose
tckTest - Runs Native Image tests for all matching coordinates (TCK)
test - Aggregates tests configured by the TCK harness
testAllInfra - Determines one artifact coordinate via generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix (or uses -Pcoordinate/-Pcoordinates if provided), then runs testInfra for that coordinate and also for 1/64. Options: -Pparallelism to control concurrency.
testInfra - Runs clean and pullAllowedDockerImages, then runs (validateIndexFiles, checkstyle, spotlessCheck, checkMetadataFiles, fetchExistingLibrariesWithNewerVersions, test, jacocoTestReport, listLibraryJars, generateDynamicAccessReport, generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport, generateLibraryStats, listTopCoordinatesByMetric, generateTopCoordinatesByMetricMatrix, listCoordinates, generateDependencyGraph, splitTestOnlyMetadata) concurrently with isolated logs for a single coordinate.
                        Options: -Pcoordinate or -Pcoordinates to specify the target; -Pparallelism to control the number of concurrent tasks.
